{
  "stem": "2522.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in the middle of that freight train the Germans had on a flat car a sandbag, machine gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It started immediately shooting flares, and it started raking the field with machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was pretty stupid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "First, they were shooting too high because these were incendiary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So you could see that they were-- they were raking it too high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You see, they were on an embankment, so you don't-- haven't got the right angle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Although if you would have gotten further out, they would have had you in the line of fire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The second thing is when they shoot a flare, I don't know if you ever-- you know how-- you hear a pop before the flare gets up, so it takes about three seconds for the flare to get up and open the parachute.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So all you have to do is when you hear a pop, you just go flat and just sit there, hoping that they don't discover you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Luckily-- again, just stupid luck-- the thing was so muddy, that I was so covered with mud that when I hit the ground, you know, apparently they didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this went on for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apparently, they were shooting high towards the edge of the forest because they felt that we must be hidden.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were raking the edge of the forest rather than the field, and this went on for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God, you know, like, 36 hours, so far as I'm concerned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I mean, I don't know how I made those 500 yards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, I've been there since then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've measured it and so forth, so I know pretty well the lay of the land.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
